    ns1:otherInformation """The course is divided in two independent parts that can be lectured in any order:

- 3D design, optimization and Monte-Carlo (Fernando Barrio)

- Signal processing with Matlab (Cristina Montalvo)
Either the course begins with 3D design or with Signal processing with Matlab. This will depend on the schedule of the professors."""@es ;
